            . I live in Prince's-street, Wapping, and am a <rs id="t18321129-144-viclabel821" type="occupation">coal-merchant</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18321129-144-victim1369 t18321129-144-viclabel821"></join>. On the 27th of October, between two and three o'clock, I was in <placeName id="t18321129-144-crimeloc822">George-yard, Whitechapel</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18321129-144-crimeloc822" type="placeName" value="George-yard, Whitechapel"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18321129-144-crimeloc822" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18321129-144-off819 t18321129-144-crimeloc822"></join>; I had some coals to deliver there - I left my coat in the head of my waggon; I saw the prisoner running away with it - I pursued, but he got out of sight- I informed a Police-officer, and saw him in custody on the 5th of November; I know he is the person.</p>
               <p>Prisoner. Q. What do you know me by? A. By seeing you many times before in Whitechapel and Georgeyard.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18321129-144-person1371">
                  ISABELLA 
                  LUCK
               <interp inst="t18321129-144-person1371" type="surname" value="LUCK"></interp>
