                     <interp inst="t18321129-144-person1374" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . He said he understood a small boy took it from the waggon - I had seen the prisoner in a black coat, grey trousers, and a cap, as the little girl has described; but I afterwards saw another boy with the prisoner's coat on, and the prisoner had a flannel jacket.</p>
